4 data-cid=\"49429214\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/Q_____Q/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u46784776-8.jpg\" alt=\"空白\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-18 00:14:30</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/Q_____Q/\" class=\"  \">空白</a>  (wayfaring stranger)\n        </div>\n\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">感谢《受戒》让人第一次觉得文字原来可以这么美。高考压力下的三年，除了金镛的家仇国恨，古惑仔的脑残傻逼，还有这样一个美好如桃花源的文字世界可以慰藉做不玩的卷子。</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u46784776 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49429214\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除空白的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49429283 data-cid=\"49429283\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/144906475/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u144906475-2.jpg\" alt=\"杜森\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-18 00:21:47</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/144906475/\" class=\"  \">杜森</a>  (得句疑人有 看书不厌忘)\n        </div>\n\n            \n                \n                <div class=\"reply-quote\">\n                <span class=\"short\">尽管随着年岁的变化，我们会对一些书、一些作家有了不同的见解，甚至隔膜、讨厌、失望，但每一本</span>\n                <span class=\"all\">尽管随着年岁的变化，我们会对一些书、一些作家有了不同的见解，甚至隔膜、讨厌、失望，但每一本书，都曾是滋养过我们独特的养分，曾是某一段岁月里果腹的食粮，充盈了些许琐碎的人生，带来一点感动。于是原谅了曾经看余秋雨郭敬明安妮宝贝的自己……</span>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"toggle-reply\">\n                    <span class=\"expaned\">...</span>\n                </a><span class=\"pubdate\"><a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/63038833/\">叶舟</a></span></div>\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">嗯，这种变化挺多的，象我前两天写洗澡，想起来金庸《书剑恩仇录》里写过陈家洛看香香公主洗澡，我找出来看看。一看，啊？这一段怎么写得那么糟糕。当年金庸每本书我都看过三四遍，可能当时主要是荷尔蒙阅读吧。</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u144906475 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49429283\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除杜森的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49429308 data-cid=\"49429308\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/71680340/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg\" alt=\"#@@#\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-18 00:26:22</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/71680340/\" class=\"  \">#@@#</a> \n        </div>\n\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">可能你没有系统读过汪曾祺，他在文论中一直提倡写作者要学习西方文艺，他认为是屠格涅夫和沈从文让他想要写作，早期作品也深受阿索林和伍尔芙影响，晚年比较主张回到民族传统，但是坚决反对“越是民族的就越是世界”的观点</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u71680340 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49429308\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除#@@#的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49429368 data-cid=\"4942