 data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/shenmedouhao/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3325271-6.jpg\" alt=\"什么都好\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-18 12:56:45</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/shenmedouhao/\" class=\"  \">什么都好</a> \n        </div>\n\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">看了题目进来......如你所说，是扯得够远的。哈哈哈哈哈。\r<br/>汪曾祺于我，只得一部《受戒》，读的时候正当好年华，深深叹服。后来有意无意不再读他其它作品。我有时觉得，阅读似乎也不是越宽泛越好，有时也需要收敛，尤其在得一珍味之后。------这完全是随性而为，没什么道理可细说。</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u3325271 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49433192\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除什么都好的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49433201 data-cid=\"49433201\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/shenmedouhao/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3325271-6.jpg\" alt=\"什么都好\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-18 12:58:32</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/shenmedouhao/\" class=\"  \">什么都好</a> \n        </div>\n\n            \n                \n                <div class=\"reply-quote\">\n                <span class=\"short\">\r\n扫荡过屠格涅夫所有小说的人有资格说一句：屠格涅夫是文体家。圆熟、明亮、落英缤纷。\r\n汪曾祺</span>\n                <span class=\"all\">\r\n扫荡过屠格涅夫所有小说的人有资格说一句：屠格涅夫是文体家。圆熟、明亮、落英缤纷。\r\n汪曾祺喜欢屠格涅夫，我很满意。</span>\n   