dmin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49459615\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除π_π的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49462160 data-cid=\"49462160\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161593207/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u161593207-1.jpg\" alt=\"+v:t4g674\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-20 14:20:35</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161593207/\" class=\"  \">+v:t4g674</a> \n        </div>\n\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">感谢《受戒》让人第一次觉得文字原来可以这么美。高考压力下的三年，除了金镛的家仇国恨，古惑仔的脑残傻逼，还有这样一个美好如桃花源的文字世界可以慰藉做不玩的卷子。</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n          <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/doubanapp/\" class=\"comment-source\" target=\"_blank\">来自豆瓣App</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u161593207 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49462160\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除+v:t4g674的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49462167 data-cid=\"49462167\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161593207/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u161593207-1.jpg\" alt=\"+v:t4g674\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-20 14:21:50</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161593207/\" class=\"  \">+v:t4g674</a> \n        </div>\n\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">尽管随着年岁的变化，我们会对一些书、一些作家有了不同的见解，甚至隔膜、讨厌、失望，但每一本书，都曾是滋养过我们独特的养分，曾是某一段岁月里果腹的食粮，充盈了些许琐碎的人生，带来一点感动。于是原谅了曾经看余秋雨郭敬明安妮宝贝的自己……</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n          <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/doubanapp/\" class=\"comment-source\" target=\"_blank\">来自豆瓣App</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u161593207 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49462167\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除+v:t4g674的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49464535 data-cid=\"49464535\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/152562687/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u152562687-1.jpg\" alt=\"爱茶的吃货君\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-20 19:29:53</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/152562687/\" class=\"  \">爱茶的吃货君</a> \n        </div>\n\n            \n                \n                <div class=\"reply-quote\">\n                <span class=\"short\">也唱几句反调吧，对事不对人，也是文科生的一点小意见吧。说“文学弄臣”有点过了，以前喜欢今天</span>\n                <span class=\"all\">也唱几句反调吧，对事不对人，也是文科生的一点小意见吧。说“文学弄臣”有点过了，以前喜欢今天看不上，也许是眼光高远了也许是旧日情怀不在，不过无论如何都不用用这么刻薄的标签吧。当时汪的正式编制就在京剧院，江青点名让他写剧本，是不是他辞职才不算弄臣呢？那个时候体制是铁板一块，他辞职的话他一家三个孩子吃什么？运动画了句号，后人给风暴中的人贴标签很容易，可是在漩涡当中，弄臣和铁骨铮铮之间的差别有时候也很被动。汪和沈之间没法比较，说是师生，写作这种师生跟风清扬和令狐冲的关系还是挺不一样的。汪有一篇专门讲“我的师承”，个人关系上他对沈是有些崇拜和感激，写作上不是一味的继承。说汪曾祺和阿成开倒车我也不能同意，这个黑锅太大了这两位背不了。汪不是一位文体家，一个作家写作有自己的特色和开创文体是两码事。汪曾祺晚年说过自己“不开风气不为师”，他在这方面没有野心，对于他自己写作的局限他也很清楚。钱钟书算不算一位作家我觉得还有待商榷，我觉得在creative writing方面他比汪曾祺才华差得太远了。要说他是学者呢他也不算现代意义上的scholar，他的定位是比较奇怪的。不过这是题外话。</span>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"toggle-reply\">\n                    <span class=\"expaned\">...</span>\n                </a><span class=\"pubdate\"><a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/65012122/\">夏安</a></span></div>\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">赞同</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n          <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/doubanapp/\" class=\"comment-source\" target=\"_blank\">来自豆瓣App</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u152562687 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49464535\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除爱茶的吃货君的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49472660 data-cid=\"49472660\" data-target_id=\"620809300\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161084677/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u161084677-1.jpg\" alt=\"猫小贤\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-21 19:18:34</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161084677/\" class=\"  \">猫小贤</a> \n        </div>\n\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">记忆最深的还是边城</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n          <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/doubanapp/\" class=\"comment-source\" target=\"_blank\">来自豆瓣App</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u161084677 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620809300/remove_comment?cid=49472660\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除猫小贤的发言?\">删除</a>\n            