lass=\"expaned\">...</span>\n                </a><span class=\"pubdate\"><a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/Kanonedeath/\">Andata</a></span></div>\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">艺术本来就不应该存在阶级性，如果艺术不走下神坛，那么艺术的意义是什么呢？</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u4901458 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620495533/remove_comment?cid=49471079\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除迷荼的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49471084 data-cid=\"49471084\" data-target_id=\"620495533\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161635017/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u161635017-2.jpg\" alt=\"那時的溫柔\"/></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content report-comment\">\n        <div class=\"author\">\n            <span class=\"\">2017-05-21 16:02:11</span>\n            <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/161635017/\" class=\"  \">那時的溫柔</a> \n        </div>\n\n\n        \n        <p class=\"\">很立体</p>\n\n        <div class=\"op-lnks\">\n        \n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"group_banned\">\n            <span class=\"gact hidden p_u161635017 p_admin p_intern fright\">&gt;\n                <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/620495533/remove_comment?cid=49471084\" class=\"j a_confirm_link\" title=\"删除那時的溫柔的发言?\">删除</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    \n\n<div class=\"comment-item\" id=49471114 data-cid=\"49471114\" data-target_id=\"620495533\" data-target_kind=\"1015\">\n    \n    <div class=\"pic\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/153179058/\"><img width=\"48\" height=\"48\" class=\"\" src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u153179058-4